==象征意义==
在[[基督|基督]][[数秘术|数秘术]]中，888代指[[耶稣|耶稣]]，有时又特别代指“救世主基督”（{{lang|en|Christ the Redeemer}}）。这种表示方法一说来源于将耶稣的名字的原文所对应的数字相加而得出<ref>{{citation|title=Numerology: Or What Pythagoras Wrought|series=[[Mathematical_Association_of_America|MAA]] Spectrum|first=Underwood|last=Dudley|publisher=Cambridge University Press|year=1997|isbn=9780883855249|page=105|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=udptayxY2E8C&pg=PA105|accessdate=2015-12-08|archive-date=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630111219/http://books.google.com/books?id=udptayxY2E8C&pg=PA105|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另一说称这个数字与[[兽名数目|兽名数目]][[666|666]]的意义正好相反<ref>{{citation|title=Book Of Fate And Fortune: Numerology And Astrology|author=Cheiro|publisher=Orient Paperbacks|year=2005|isbn=9788122200461|page=60|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=464XH0LOCEgC&pg=PA60|accessdate=2015-12-08|archive-date=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630111025/http://books.google.com/books?id=464XH0LOCEgC&pg=PA60|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[中国|中国]]，888是一个吉利的象征。数字8在标准汉语中音同“发”，三个8组合在一起代表着富贵与吉祥<ref>{{citation|title=Understanding Information Systems: What They Do and Why We Need Them|first=Lee|last=Ratzan|publisher=American Library Association|year=2004|isbn=9780838908686|page=202|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=lrdRYCRjUZUC&pg=PA202|accessdate=2015-12-08|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511161546/http://books.google.com/books?id=lrdRYCRjUZUC&pg=PA202|dead-url=no}}</ref>。正因如此，在中国，数字“8”连续出现三次或以上的电话号码会被视为幸运号码，同时受到许多人的欢迎<ref>{{citation|title=Working Across Cultures|first=John|last=Hooker|publisher=Stanford University Press|year=2003|isbn=9780804748070|page=191|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=wJXo_mOXd1IC&pg=PA191|accessdate=2015-12-08|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511151837/http://books.google.com/books?id=wJXo_mOXd1IC&pg=PA191|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

